{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/manga-lawas-itoshi-no-irene-diadaptasi-dalam-bentuk-live-action/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Manga lawas Itoshi no Irene Diadaptasi dalam Bentuk Live-Action","content":"<p>Jepang seolah tidak pernah kehabisan dalam mewujudkan ide-ide kreatif yang dapat menjadikan  sesuatu yang bisa dinikmati oleh masyarakat. Industri manga, misalnya. Ketika pembaca manga lebih terbatas dan ada manga dengan cerita yang cukup baik dan unik, ada peluang untuk diadaptasi ke dalam format lain seperti anime atau film <em>live-action</em> supaya masyarakat yang tidak membaca manga bisa turut menikmati ceritanya, sehingga pasarnya menjadi semakin luas. Tidak terkecuali Itoshi no Irene.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49256\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49256\" data-attachment-id=\"49256\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/manga-lawas-itoshi-no-irene-diadaptasi-dalam-bentuk-live-action/attachment/itoshi1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"itoshi1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Manga Itoshi no Irene (Sumber: myanimelist.net)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49256\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49256\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Manga Itoshi no Irene (Sumber: myanimelist.net)</p></div></p>\n<p>Manga besutan Hideki Arai ini terbit pada tahun 1995 hingga 1996 oleh majalah Shogakukan, yang kemudian diproduksi sebanyak 6 volume terpisah. Manga ini bercerita tentang kehidupan seorang wanita asing bernama Irene yang tinggal di desa miskin di Jepang. Irene yang menikah dengan Iwao berusaha beradaptasi dengan lingkungannya yang baru, berbaur dengan penduduk desa, dan dikenal banyak orang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49249\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49249\" data-attachment-id=\"49249\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/manga-lawas-itoshi-no-irene-diadaptasi-dalam-bentuk-live-action/attachment/itoshi2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"itoshi2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Visual Itoshi no Irene (Sumber: irene-movie.jp)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49249\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49249\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Visual Itoshi no Irene (Sumber: irene-movie.jp)</p></div></p>\n<p>Pada awal tahun 2018, Shogakukan mengumumkan kalau proses produksi adaptasi Itoshi no Irene sudah dimulai, ditandai dengan pembukaan website resmi dan media sosialnya. Keisuke Yoshida—yang pernah memimpin pembuatan film <em>live-action</em> Silver Spoon dan Himeanoru—didaulat memimpin proses produksi film ini. Dia pun mencari artis hingga ke Filipina dan didapatlah bintang baru bernama Shitoi Nattsu yang akan berperan sebagai Irene.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49250\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49250\" data-attachment-id=\"49250\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/manga-lawas-itoshi-no-irene-diadaptasi-dalam-bentuk-live-action/attachment/itoshi3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"itoshi3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Para pemeran Itoshi no Irene (Sumber: irene-movie.jp)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49250\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49250\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Para pemeran Itoshi no Irene (Sumber: irene-movie.jp)</p></div></p>\n<p>Iwao Shishido, sang karakter utama yang meninggalkan desanya lalu kembali membawa calon pendamping wanitanya yaitu Irene, akan diperankan oleh aktor senior Ken Yasuda. Pengalamannya di adaptasi <em>live-action</em> seperti Hentai Kamen, Kuroshitsuji, dan Gintama, juga serial drama seperti Hotaru no Hikari, Minna! Esper Dayo, dan Aoi Honoo diharapkan dapat mengangkat kualitas dari film bergenre drama komedi romantis ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49251\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49251\" data-attachment-id=\"49251\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/manga-lawas-itoshi-no-irene-diadaptasi-dalam-bentuk-live-action/attachment/itoshi4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"itoshi4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Irene yang ekspresif membawa kehangatan suasana (Sumber: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49251\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49251\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Irene yang ekspresif membawa kehangatan suasana (Sumber: youtube.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Jalinan cerita yang mengangkat kehidupan penduduk desa sederhana di Jepang membuat kita bisa melihat negara matahari terbit itu dari sudut pandang yang lain. Kehidupan glamor nan sibuk ala Tokyo jelas tidak menjadi topik utama yang diangkat. Apalagi, <em>setting</em> waktu tahun 90’an dapat membuat penontonnya mengenang masa kanak-kanak mereka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49252\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49252\" data-attachment-id=\"49252\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/manga-lawas-itoshi-no-irene-diadaptasi-dalam-bentuk-live-action/attachment/itoshi5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"itoshi5\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Iwao pun akhirnya bisa tersenyum di hadapan istrinya (Sumber: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49252\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49252\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Iwao pun akhirnya bisa tersenyum di hadapan istrinya (Sumber: youtube.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Suasana pedesaan yang cenderung santai menjadi sajian utama. Dari segi tokoh, kehidupan pengantin baru yang memulai hidup dari nol akan mewarnai film dan membuat para pasangan menjadi iri akan kesederhanaan, ekspresi bahagia, dan ketulusan yang ditunjukkan. Para pengantin ataupun pasangan yang ingin melanjutkan ke jenjang pernikahan bisa meniru sikap yang ditunjukkan oleh pasangan Irene dan Iwao dalam film ini.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FJi5Csam_TM\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Trailer Itoshi no Irene</em></p>\n<p>Jika kalian telah menonton trailer di atas, apa yang dapat kalian simpulkan? Dua pasangan romantis yang saling melengkapi. Irene yang ceria dan ekspresif berhadapan dengan Iwao yang pendiam dan irit tawa. Perjalanan mereka pun menjadi tidak hambar dan penuh dengan hal menarik. Sayangnya, film ini baru akan tayang pada 14 September 2018 dan belum ada kepastian kapan tayang di Indonesia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49253\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49253\" data-attachment-id=\"49253\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/manga-lawas-itoshi-no-irene-diadaptasi-dalam-bentuk-live-action/attachment/itoshi6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"itoshi6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Romantisme pasangan yang baru menikah membuat iri sekitarnya (Sumber: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49253\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/itoshi6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49253\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Romantisme pasangan yang baru menikah membuat iri sekitarnya (Sumber: youtube.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Apakah kalian iri dengan kisah seperti ini? Kalian juga bisa lo membuat kisah hidup kalian semenarik mungkin. Jika perlu, tuangkan dalam suatu cerita dan buatlah komik, kemudian kirimkan ke <a href=\"mailto:submission@ciayo.com\">submission@ciayo.com</a>. Kalian bisa juga mengikuti <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-challenge-vol-3-total-hadiahnya-450-juta-rupiah/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics <em>C</em><em>hallenge</em></a> untuk mendapatkan berbagai hadiah menarik! Lagipula, siapa tahu cerita kalian akan bisa diadaptasi dalam bentuk anime dan film? Ayo, berkaryalah!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b2b498a9-9a41-57a7-8785-a22c65c0fb08"}}}